3
00:00:38,430 --> 00:00:40,307
Zovem se Richard.

4
00:00:42,230 --> 00:00:44,141
Što vas još zanima?

5
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:47,218
Moja obitelj? lli odakle sam?

6
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:49,461
To nije bitno.

7
00:00:51,150 --> 00:00:53,869
Ni kada prijedeš ocean
i otkvaciš se,

8
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:57,786
tražeci nešto
ljepše, uzbudljivije,

9
00:00:58,590 --> 00:01:01,058
i, priznajem,
nešto opasnije.

10
00:01:02,790 --> 00:01:05,463
Poslije 1 8 sati
u zrakoplovu,

11
00:01:05,630 --> 00:01:07,939
3 glupa filma,
2 plasticna jela,

12
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:10,265
6 piva, bez sna,

13
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:13,108
slijecem

14
00:01:13,430 --> 00:01:15,182
u Bangkok.

15
00:01:15,430 --> 00:01:17,386
Želite do vodopada
i tržnice na vodi?

16
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:19,700
Za vas, 1500.

17
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:24,143
Trebaš smještaj?
-Ne, hvala, sam cu se snaci.

18
00:01:25,030 --> 00:01:27,339
To je to. Bangkok.

19
00:01:27,550 --> 00:01:31,179
Grad užitaka.
Vrata Jl Azije.

20
00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:36,260
Hrpe dolara i maraka
za krivotvorene satove.

21
00:01:38,590 --> 00:01:40,820
Tu se gladni
dolaze nahraniti.

22
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:42,747
Hoceš zmijsku krv?

23
00:01:43,470 --> 00:01:46,268
Rekao si zmijsku
krv? -Da.

24
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:51,098
Ne, hvala. -Zašto ne?

25
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:54,740
Ne svida mi se ta
ideja. -Možda se bojiš?

26
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:58,505
Bojiš se necega novog?
-Ne. Ne svida mi se ideja.

27
00:01:58,750 --> 00:02:04,029
Turisti vole sigurnost,
ha, americki decko?

28
00:02:06,710 --> 00:02:09,178
Nikad nemojte odbiti poziv.

29
00:02:09,950 --> 00:02:11,986
Ne opirite se Nepoznatom.

30
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:31,263
Uvijek budite ljubazni.
Gospodo,

31
00:02:31,990 --> 00:02:33,503
ovo je sjajno.

32
00:02:34,070 --> 00:02:36,538
Nemojte ostati
predugo u gostima.

33
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:41,787
Budite otvoreni novim
stvarima i iskustvima.

34
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,782
Ako vas i zaboli,

35
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:46,420
vjerojatno se ipak isplati.

36
00:02:49,350 --> 00:02:52,342
Dobra vecer. -Bog.
Mogu dobiti sobu?

37
00:03:09,670 --> 00:03:12,548
Jedino je koma
što svi misle isto;

38
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:17,745
prijedemo pola svijeta,
a onda gledamo TV,

39
00:03:17,830 --> 00:03:20,298
u hotelu sa svim
pogodnostima.

40
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:22,301
Moraš se upitati...

41
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:25,582
"Zacas cemo sve
srediti, bez brige."

42
00:03:25,790 --> 00:03:27,826
...koja je svrha?

43
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,868
Hvala.

44
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:11,944
(laku noc.)

45
00:04:16,710 --> 00:04:20,180
A ako moraš putovati
sam... jebiga.

46
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:23,947
Ako tako mora biti,
onda tako jest.

47
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:29,179
ŽAl

48
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:51,065
Svi sretni?

49
00:04:53,350 --> 00:04:57,582
Svi se zabavljate?
Jebite se!

50
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,740
Paraziti odvratni!

51
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,588
Paraziti!

52
00:05:05,790 --> 00:05:08,987
Ma super! Jebite se!
Gori ste od raka!

53
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:20,380
Debele svinje proždiru
cijeli jebeni svijet!

54
00:05:27,230 --> 00:05:29,221
Hej, ti!

55
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:37,066
lmaš što za pušiti?
-Ne. Nemam ništa.

56
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:43,228
Nema frke. lmam ja svašta.

57
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:03,259
Kužiš me? -Aha.

58
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:06,221
Vraga kužiš.

59
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:09,181
Tocno, ne kužim.

60
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:14,985
Odmah je bolje!

61
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,941
Hvala.

62
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:25,748
Žal je kriv, kužiš? Žal.

63
00:06:26,670 --> 00:06:29,309
Prelijep je.

64
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:32,786
Previše podražaja.
Previše... uzbudenja.

65
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:35,339
Nastojim to potisnuti,
ali ne ide.

66
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:40,821
Znaš...

67
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:43,260
nalazi se na Otoku.

68
00:06:44,350 --> 00:06:49,902
A Otok je savršen.
Presavršen.

69
00:06:50,110 --> 00:06:54,342
l zbilja ne mislim samo
``Baš zgodno``.

70
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:57,658
ludnica do jaja!

71
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:01,346
Savršen.

72
00:07:01,790 --> 00:07:07,820
To je... jedna laguna
okružena stijenama.

73
00:07:07,990 --> 00:07:10,550
Potpuno skrovita, potpuno...

74
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:13,460
zabranjena.

75
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:17,464
l nitko nikada
ne može otici onamo.

76
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:22,302
Ali neki su otišli.
Nekoc davno.

77
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:29,623
ljudi s idealima.
Kužiš? Ne obicni, turisticki,

78
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:32,463
jebeni kreteni.

79
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:35,588
Vjeruješ da takvo
mjesto postoji? -Ne.

80
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:38,824
Misliš da bih
morao vjerovati?

81
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:47,269
Nije važno što ja mislim.

82
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:50,107
To ti odlucuješ.

83
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:55,388
ldeali... Jebeni paraziti!

84
00:07:55,590 --> 00:07:58,024
Debele svinje!

85
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:05,704
Ja sam htio
smisliti lijek.

86
00:08:06,950 --> 00:08:09,100
Spasiti žal.

87
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:12,299
Rekoh im, ``Morate otici.``

88
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:15,385
``Morate otici odavde.``

89
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,981
Ali tko me sluša.

90
00:08:22,990 --> 00:08:25,265
Nemoj zamjeriti, ali...

91
00:08:26,670 --> 00:08:29,230
Ti si malo
sjeban u glavu, ne?

92
00:08:42,950 --> 00:08:44,588
Uzmi, Richard.

93
00:08:48,430 --> 00:08:50,182
Bilo mi je drago.

94
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:53,748
l meni.

95
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:22,064
Pazite! Struja.

96
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:24,782
Gospodo!

97
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:28,620
Ohladi. Nema frke.

98
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:40,265
Hej. lma pismo za tebe.

99
00:09:40,710 --> 00:09:43,782
Što? -Pismo. Na vratima.

100
00:10:05,830 --> 00:10:09,664
Jebote, karta...!

101
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:12,342
Vi...

102
00:10:28,310 --> 00:10:30,141
lma koga?

103
00:11:03,110 --> 00:11:06,625
Nadaš se, sanjaš,

104
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:12,702
ali ne vjeruješ
da ce ti se išta dogoditi.

105
00:11:14,230 --> 00:11:16,505
Nije to ko na filmu.

106
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,460
A kada se što dogodi,

107
00:11:23,110 --> 00:11:25,419
ocekuješ da ce
biti drukcije,

108
00:11:27,950 --> 00:11:29,986
snažnije,

109
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,301
stvarnije.

110
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:42,065
Cekao sam da me lupi.

111
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:46,982
Ali ne!

112
00:11:48,310 --> 00:11:51,985
lme: Paško Patak.
Mjesto rodenja: Snokraj.

113
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:54,584
Ovo ce nas jebati.

114
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:57,463
Policija je
ispitala sve goste,

115
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:59,501
ali nisu gnjavili.

116
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:02,582
Potpišite izjavu.

117
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:16,063
U redu je. Piše, prerezao je
vene. Našli ste ga mrtvoga.

118
00:12:17,710 --> 00:12:20,508
Nisu pitali za kartu...

119
00:12:20,710 --> 00:12:23,907
Nema problema.
Pa je nisam spominjao.

120
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,821
Ugodan dan želim.

121
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:38,622
Sretno.

122
00:12:45,110 --> 00:12:47,146
Cujte... mislim...

123
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:51,303
Taj Otok možda ni ne postoji.

124
00:12:51,470 --> 00:12:54,223
Možda ni ne možemo
stici onamo.

125
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:57,302
Samo me zanimalo
biste li išli sa mnom.

126
00:13:12,310 --> 00:13:14,346
Ne bi se izgubio?

127
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:18,783
Mislim, na izlet.
S curom i sa mnom?

128
00:13:18,950 --> 00:13:21,305
Mislim, vas dvoje i ja.

129
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:24,741
Na tajni otok. Bog.

130
00:13:29,710 --> 00:13:32,543
Svi žele uciniti
nešto drugo,

131
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:34,980
a ipak ucine isto.

132
00:13:38,710 --> 00:13:42,783
Shvatio sam da nemam
pojma kako stici onamo.

133
00:13:45,310 --> 00:13:49,622
Ali Etienne, moram
mu priznati, bio je super.

134
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:54,028
Sve je organizirao.
Karte. Prijevoz. Cijeli put.

135
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:58,422
Bangkok-Surat Thani.
Odande u Na Thon.

136
00:13:58,590 --> 00:14:03,380
Na Thon-Chaweng.
800 km u 24 sata.

137
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:08,260
Za manje od 400 bahta.
lzvrsna cijena.

138
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:16,380
Krenuli smo prema
Nepoznatom,

139
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:20,020
iako uobicajenom
turistickom rutom.

140
00:14:49,070 --> 00:14:52,585
Sve sredeno. Sutra
ujutro. 1800 bahta.

141
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:57,101
Svaka cast. -Ali
nece nas odvesti na otok.

142
00:14:57,270 --> 00:15:01,388
To je zabranjeni
nacionalni park. -Ali...

143
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:06,107
Na ovome možemo
prenociti. Ali...

144
00:15:06,270 --> 00:15:09,307
To nije taj otok. -Znam.

145
00:15:09,470 --> 00:15:12,621
A odavde do Otoka...
-Plivamo.

146
00:15:13,190 --> 00:15:15,499
Plivamo?! -Da.

147
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:18,309
Ostavimo ruksake na
ovom otoku, i plivamo.

148
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:22,269
Znaš plivati, ne?
-Jasno da znam.

149
00:15:22,510 --> 00:15:25,502
Onda nema frke.
-Koliko je daleko?

150
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:29,862
Kilometar-dva.
-Ah. Prava sitnica...!

151
00:15:30,110 --> 00:15:34,945
Daj! lsplatit ce se. Prava
pustolovina. Samo nas troje.

152
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:48,068
Znaš plivati? Jasno.

153
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:51,302
Ja sam Francuz
i imam zgodnu curu.

154
00:15:54,670 --> 00:15:56,342
Super!

155
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:59,383
K vragu! -Ne možeš unutra?

156
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:06,186
lzgubio si kljuc?

157
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:10,588
Sranje. -Da, sranje.

158
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:13,705
Jesi za pivo?

159
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:26,820
Bolje ti je bez nje. -Otkud
ti znaš? Nisi je ni upoznao.

160
00:16:26,950 --> 00:16:29,862
Želim mu pomoci
da preživi komu.

161
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:34,298
Nisam više u komi.
-Vidiš, Zeph? Nije.

162
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:36,540
Mijenjamo temu.

163
00:16:36,990 --> 00:16:41,222
Može o tome kako 1 sat
visiš pred zrcalom?

164
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:45,782
Ovaj tip voli
brisati guzicu lišcem.

165
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:49,509
Misli da je
komandos iz džungle.

166
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:52,827
Ma hajde. -Jebote!

167
00:16:53,590 --> 00:16:58,266
Znaš ono kad je curi
serviran miš umjesto piceka?

168
00:16:59,910 --> 00:17:06,258
Zagrize batak, a kad ono -
miš! Tocno? -Aha.

169
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:09,308
Svi pricaju o tome.

170
00:17:09,470 --> 00:17:12,906
To se uvijek dogodi
frendu frendova frenda.

171
00:17:13,190 --> 00:17:18,548
Pa? -Pa... l ovdje svi
o necemu pricaju -

172
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:21,225
o Žalu.

173
00:17:24,470 --> 00:17:27,462
A Žal savršen, covjece.

174
00:17:27,870 --> 00:17:32,466
Na Otoku je.
Ne vidi se s mora.

175
00:17:32,990 --> 00:17:36,983
Zamisli samo...
Bijeli pijesak.

176
00:17:37,150 --> 00:17:41,940
Kristalno cisto more. Palme.
-Kokosi i ostalo.

177
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:45,228
Reci mu najbolji
dio. -Usto...

178
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:50,106
Marihuane ko drva. Pušiš
cijeli dan, svaki dan.

179
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:53,899
Do kraja života!
-ludnica od trave!

180
00:17:55,270 --> 00:18:00,264
Samo par ljudi zna gdje
je. l nikome nece reci.

181
00:18:00,430 --> 00:18:03,900
Jasno, nitko ne zna
te koji znaju.

182
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:06,902
Prica o pecenom mišu...!

183
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:10,108
Da ja znam gdje
je takvo mjesto,

184
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:14,223
i ja bih tajio. Tko bi htio

185
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:17,660
da ti banu kretenski turisti!?

186
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:21,704
Što misliš o prici?

187
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:26,622
Dobra je.

188
00:18:27,150 --> 00:18:28,788
Dobra prica.

189
00:18:29,510 --> 00:18:31,341
lmam tvoj kljuc!

190
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:37,230
lako to nije
bio dio plana,

191
00:18:37,390 --> 00:18:40,302
odlucio sam im
ostaviti kopiju karte.

192
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:43,701
To nije bila
baš mudra odluka...

193
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:48,504
Rekoh, svi putnici
šire dobre vijesti.

194
00:18:50,150 --> 00:18:52,220
No da budem iskren,

195
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:55,586
bio sam poput drugih -

196
00:18:56,470 --> 00:18:59,143
usran od straha
od Nepoznatog.

197
00:18:59,470 --> 00:19:02,542
Odlucan ponijeti
nešto poznato...

198
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:16,229
Richard?

199
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:19,542
Spreman? -Evo me.

200
00:19:21,990 --> 00:19:23,628
ldemo.

201
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:25,502
Francoise? -Etienne ce
poludjeti ako ga probudim!

202
00:20:25,670 --> 00:20:28,230
Misli da gubim vrijeme
snimajuci nebo.

203
00:20:37,790 --> 00:20:41,749
Slažem se. -Da? Pogledaj.

204
00:20:44,950 --> 00:20:47,418
Jednom cu snimiti
savršenu fotku.

205
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:17,305
Znaš li
da u beskonacnosti svemira

206
00:21:19,990 --> 00:21:22,345
zacijelo postoji neki planet

207
00:21:23,670 --> 00:21:27,629
baš poput ovoga
gdje neko bice poput tebe

208
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:30,588
snima nas tu dolje.

209
00:21:31,190 --> 00:21:36,059
U biti, snimaš samu sebe
u paralelnom svemiru.

210
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:38,585
Nevjerojatno.

211
00:21:40,510 --> 00:21:43,263
Postoji bezbroj svjetova

212
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:46,024
gdje se svašta
može dogoditi.

213
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:49,985
Dogada se. -Znaš što?

214
00:21:50,470 --> 00:21:53,428
To su pretenciozna
sranja koja Ameri

215
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:57,099
uvaljuju Francuskinjama
da ih uvuku u krevet.

216
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:01,906
Zaboga. Oprosti.

217
00:22:02,150 --> 00:22:04,300
Mislio sam da
dobro napredujem...

218
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:06,984
To je samo nebo. Pokušaj.

219
00:22:18,430 --> 00:22:22,708
Kada ti se netko
svidi, nadeš razloga

220
00:22:22,870 --> 00:22:25,384
vjerovati da je to
prava osoba za tebe.

221
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:28,864
Ne treba ti
dobar razlog.

222
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:32,107
l snimanje neba
nocu može proci.

223
00:22:32,430 --> 00:22:35,024
A na kraju ispadne

224
00:22:35,190 --> 00:22:37,829
da cete upravo
zbog toga prekinuti.

225
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:41,229
No u fazi zaljubljivanja

226
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:44,547
misliš da si upravo
to oduvijek tražio.

227
00:22:51,390 --> 00:22:54,746
Jedan kilometar. -Dva.
-Richard?

228
00:22:55,550 --> 00:22:58,508
Ne znam.
Amerikanac sam. -Pa?

229
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:03,063
Mi racunamo u miljama.
-Dakle, koliko je to milja?

230
00:23:04,350 --> 00:23:07,069
Ne znam. Ali cini se daleko.

231
00:23:08,670 --> 00:23:10,945
Ako je predaleko,
udavit cemo se.

232
00:23:15,670 --> 00:23:18,184
Ako ne pokušamo,
nikad necemo saznati.

233
00:23:18,510 --> 00:23:20,307
Tocno.

234
00:23:24,550 --> 00:23:26,700
Onda idemo!

235
00:23:59,150 --> 00:24:01,823
Dobro ste? -Jesmo.

236
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,866
Na pola smo puta.

237
00:24:08,430 --> 00:24:10,898
Jebemu! Richard!

238
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:15,147
Jebemu! -Što je? -Peraja!

239
00:24:16,190 --> 00:24:19,102
Šališ se?! -Ne! Peraja.

240
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:25,462
Morski pas? -Ne znam.
Tamo... Na oko 100 m!

241
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:31,108
Velika? -Da.

242
00:24:33,230 --> 00:24:35,460
l, što da radim?!

243
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:40,581
Ništa. Samo da znaš.
-Nisi mi trebao reci!

244
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:44,026
Žao mi je! -Sad je
malo prekasno!

245
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:57,099
Francoise!

246
00:24:57,270 --> 00:25:00,068
Nema je! -Bože!

247
00:25:00,670 --> 00:25:04,458
Što se dogodilo?!
-Nestala je pod vodom.

248
00:25:04,590 --> 00:25:06,546
Nešto ju je povuklo!

249
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:13,029
Ne vidim je.

250
00:25:13,870 --> 00:25:18,466
Njezina vreca! -Jesi li
vidio morskoga psa?

251
00:25:18,630 --> 00:25:21,144
Ne znam. Ne znam!

252
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:24,462
Jebemu!

253
00:25:42,470 --> 00:25:46,782
Europljani! Baš ste duhoviti.
Vrlo iskricav humor!

254
00:25:46,910 --> 00:25:49,708
Normalno da je vaša
komedija osvojila svijet.

255
00:25:49,950 --> 00:25:54,228
A Moliere? -Tko? Daj odjebi!

256
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:51,542
Hajde.

257
00:27:04,950 --> 00:27:06,986
Oho!

258
00:27:16,390 --> 00:27:19,188
E ovo se zove hrpa trave!

259
00:30:34,110 --> 00:30:36,544
Dakako, trebali
smo se vratiti.

260
00:30:36,710 --> 00:30:40,146
Ali nisam kanio.
Ne u tom trenutku.

261
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:44,025
Govorio sam im,
"Uspjet cemo. Vjerujte mi."

262
00:30:44,950 --> 00:30:46,622
"Tamo je raj."

263
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:50,229
Krenemo li nizvodno,
doci cemo do Zala.

264
00:30:51,870 --> 00:30:53,462
ldemo.

265
00:31:25,910 --> 00:31:28,344
Oh, Bože!

266
00:31:36,150 --> 00:31:37,947
(Sranje!)

267
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:47,067
Dakle? -Što dakle?

268
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,707
Kako cemo dolje?

269
00:31:49,870 --> 00:31:52,987
Otkud znam?! Zar sve
moram ja odluciti?!

270
00:31:53,150 --> 00:31:56,506
Skocit cemo. -Ti si
htio biti voda.

271
00:31:56,670 --> 00:32:00,299
Jer si se ti usrao
od straha, Francuzicu!

272
00:32:00,430 --> 00:32:02,990
Gle kamo si nas ti doveo!

273
00:32:03,870 --> 00:32:07,783
Skocit cemo. -Odsad
slobodno ti budi voda.

274
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:09,781
Dobro.

275
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:12,345
Onuda cemo se spustiti.

276
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:16,389
Možemo skociti.
-Francoise, necemo skociti!

277
00:32:16,630 --> 00:32:19,781
Prestani o tome.
A to sa spuštanjem...

278
00:32:19,950 --> 00:32:23,386
To je zbilja
kretenski prijedlog!

279
00:32:25,830 --> 00:32:29,140
Nazvao si me kretenom?!
-Za pocetak.

280
00:32:30,310 --> 00:32:32,949
Dodi! -Dobro, šupcino.

281
00:32:33,110 --> 00:32:35,021
Francoise!

282
00:32:39,950 --> 00:32:41,861
Francoise!

283
00:32:46,390 --> 00:32:50,747
Hajde! Nije opasno!

284
00:32:51,870 --> 00:32:56,580
Bacite vrece i skocite!
-Dobro. Skacemo.

285
00:32:57,190 --> 00:32:59,021
Jebote...

286
00:33:13,950 --> 00:33:16,020
Jesi vidio?!

287
00:33:36,430 --> 00:33:38,785
Cestitam!

288
00:33:39,550 --> 00:33:42,940
Meni je trebao 1 sat
da skupim hrabrost.

289
00:33:44,670 --> 00:33:48,458
Ali, bio sam sam. To mi je
olakšavajuca okolnost.

290
00:33:51,150 --> 00:33:53,061
Upoznat cu vas sa Sal.

291
00:33:53,990 --> 00:33:56,948
lsuse! lpak smo stigli!

292
00:34:01,630 --> 00:34:03,825
Nemoj otici.

293
00:34:29,870 --> 00:34:32,259
Ne znam što smo ocekivali.

294
00:34:32,470 --> 00:34:36,622
Ljude u spiljama. lli
možda neke u šatorima.

295
00:34:37,270 --> 00:34:40,626
Ali ovo ne!
-Bog, Keaty. Smotaj.

296
00:34:40,790 --> 00:34:43,702
Kao da smo došli
u izgubljen svijet.

297
00:34:43,990 --> 00:34:46,345
Raznoliko društvo putnika

298
00:34:46,510 --> 00:34:49,502
koji nisu u prolazu,
vec tu žive.

299
00:34:53,270 --> 00:34:57,422
Odjednom sam shvatio
da nismo pozvani.

300
00:35:04,150 --> 00:35:06,505
Tip koji je nacrtao
kartu... -Daffy.

301
00:35:08,470 --> 00:35:10,108
Mrtav je.

302
00:35:12,310 --> 00:35:15,746
Prerezao si je vene
u hotelu u Bangkoku.

303
00:35:15,910 --> 00:35:19,061
Vidio si to?
-Došao sam kasnije.

304
00:35:21,510 --> 00:35:23,466
Baš tužno.

305
00:35:24,950 --> 00:35:27,703
On je jedan od osnivaca
naše zajednice.

306
00:35:29,310 --> 00:35:31,301
Ali uhvatila ga je depresija.

307
00:35:34,950 --> 00:35:37,145
Policija nije znala
što bi s tijelom.

308
00:35:37,270 --> 00:35:39,306
Valjda ce ga spaliti.

309
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:46,459
Je li dao kartu još nekome?

310
00:35:47,910 --> 00:35:49,821
Ne bih rekao.

311
00:35:50,550 --> 00:35:53,348
Jeste li je vi
kome pokazali? -Ne.

312
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,983
Ne.

313
00:35:56,750 --> 00:35:58,342
Ne.

314
00:36:00,270 --> 00:36:01,862
Dobro.

315
00:36:03,750 --> 00:36:06,025
Poštujemo našu tajnu.

316
00:36:30,470 --> 00:36:33,940
Cuj ovo! Da rikneš!

317
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:34,018
Koja ljepota, jebote!

318
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:14,984
Pozor, narode!

319
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:21,104
Dakle... ``Sutra cu putovati
mnogo milja biciklom.``

320
00:38:22,270 --> 00:38:24,659
Vicky.

321
00:38:30,510 --> 00:38:32,705
Vrlo dobro. Helene?

322
00:38:39,350 --> 00:38:43,502
Vrlo dobro. Keaty?
-To je prejednostavno.

323
00:38:43,750 --> 00:38:46,184
Daj, molim te!

324
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:57,301
Znam ja još...

325
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,822
Richard!

326
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:12,540
To, Richard! Sad si naš.

327
00:39:17,390 --> 00:39:19,745
Ovo je postao naš svijet.

328
00:39:19,910 --> 00:39:22,504
A ovi ljudi naša obitelj.

329
00:39:23,350 --> 00:39:26,501
O domu i civilizaciji
nismo razmišljali.

330
00:39:27,390 --> 00:39:30,700
Skrasio sam se.
l našao svoj poziv:

331
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:34,104
potraga za užicima.

332
00:39:48,590 --> 00:39:52,344
Sal je bila voda,
ali bila je ko i drugi.

333
00:39:52,430 --> 00:39:54,898
Nije bilo neke ideologije
ili takvih sranja;

334
00:39:55,030 --> 00:39:59,421
samo Žal, za one koji
ne vole turisticke plaže.

335
00:40:00,070 --> 00:40:02,664
Da, gradimo.
l u raju treba raditi.

336
00:40:06,830 --> 00:40:09,503
Godinama taje o
postojanju ovoga mjesta.

337
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:13,305
Bili su sami sebi dovoljni.

338
00:40:14,470 --> 00:40:17,303
U civilizaciju su išli samo

339
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:20,383
da prodaju marihuanu
i kupe riže.

340
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:24,308
Uzgajamo marihuanu;
ne krademo farmerima

341
00:40:24,430 --> 00:40:27,900
s druge strane otoka.
-Znaju da ste tu?

342
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:32,304
Drže se svoga dijela;
ne smetamo jedni drugima.

343
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:35,467
Rekli su da mi
možemo ostati,

344
00:40:35,630 --> 00:40:38,940
ali da novi ne dolaze.
To nam svima odgovara.

345
00:40:39,110 --> 00:40:41,578
Vi ste imali srece...

346
00:40:41,750 --> 00:40:44,662
Keatyja zanimaju
samo dvije stvari:

347
00:40:44,910 --> 00:40:49,108
Hvala Ti, Bože, za
dva glavna stupa civilizacije:

348
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:53,028
kršcanstvo i kriket.

349
00:40:57,750 --> 00:41:00,822
Tri su Švedanina:
Christo, Sten i Karl.

350
00:41:00,990 --> 00:41:03,458
Volimo pecanje. -Pecanje. Da.

351
00:41:03,750 --> 00:41:06,139
A zimi volimo skijanje.

352
00:41:08,630 --> 00:41:11,303
Jasno, na Tajlandu
nema skijanja.

353
00:41:12,430 --> 00:41:16,139
Cekamo da ribe dodu.

354
00:41:20,750 --> 00:41:22,741
Jesi?

355
00:41:24,870 --> 00:41:28,499
l rekoh vam,
``Bit ce vam dano``!

356
00:41:39,110 --> 00:41:42,182
Kuharov je nadimak
Cistunko...

357
00:41:42,350 --> 00:41:45,786
lspecimo ih. -Jer je
opsjednut pranjem.

358
00:41:45,990 --> 00:41:48,185
Ribe, ribe, ribe...

359
00:41:52,670 --> 00:41:54,865
Još smrdim po ribi!

360
00:41:55,030 --> 00:41:59,581
Svatko je mogao naci sport
ili zabavu kakvu voli.

361
00:41:59,750 --> 00:42:03,709
Etienne super igra nogomet.
l ja bih mogao.

362
00:42:04,470 --> 00:42:07,223
Ali ne želim. -O cemu ti to?

363
00:42:07,910 --> 00:42:13,303
Ma bez veze. -lmaš curu?
-Tu? -Bilo gdje.

364
00:42:15,270 --> 00:42:19,707
Ne. Zašto? -Ma bez veze.

365
00:42:26,910 --> 00:42:28,980
Desna ruka iznad...

366
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:32,267
Još su 3 lopte.
Možda netko ne razumije?

367
00:42:39,910 --> 00:42:43,619
Jedino mi se nije svidio
Salin bahati decko Bugs.

368
00:42:43,750 --> 00:42:47,823
Stolar. -Richard,
znaš ovo napraviti?

369
00:42:48,630 --> 00:42:50,825
Znaš li išta napraviti?

370
00:42:51,990 --> 00:42:54,584
Muškarac mora nešto znati.

371
00:42:59,510 --> 00:43:02,308
Svaka zajednica
ima svoje obrede.

372
00:43:02,470 --> 00:43:05,462
Naš je bio jednostavan:
tko zadnji stigne,

373
00:43:05,630 --> 00:43:10,465
tetovira novoga. -Boli
ko vrag, tako da znaš.

374
00:43:10,590 --> 00:43:12,581
Što je rekao?

375
00:43:16,510 --> 00:43:18,705
Andy, približi ga!

376
00:43:26,310 --> 00:43:29,029
Bože!

377
00:43:33,590 --> 00:43:35,342
lsuse!

378
00:43:42,510 --> 00:43:45,502
Sve je bilo
zbilja ko u raju,

379
00:43:45,670 --> 00:43:47,740
osim jedne stvari;

380
00:43:47,950 --> 00:43:51,784
želja je želja,
ma gdje bio...

381
00:43:52,150 --> 00:43:56,905
Sunce je nece spržiti,
ni plima odnijeti.

382
00:44:33,790 --> 00:44:37,669
Prvo, poigrava se
tobom. -O cemu ti to?

383
00:44:37,830 --> 00:44:42,540
Drugo, ne znaš francuski.
Trece, on zna francuski.

384
00:44:42,710 --> 00:44:46,385
Zapravo, cetvrto:
on jest Francuz.

385
00:44:47,350 --> 00:44:51,662
Peto, mnogo bolje igra
nogomet od tebe.

386
00:44:52,430 --> 00:44:55,024
Šesto, ti si malo cudan.

387
00:44:55,190 --> 00:44:58,739
Neke to cure vole.
Ali ne one koje bi ti htio.

388
00:44:58,910 --> 00:45:02,505
Ma nemoj.
-Zašto te zadnja ostavila?

389
00:45:02,670 --> 00:45:06,948
Nisam ja kriv.
-Sedmo, imaš jake palceve.

390
00:45:07,110 --> 00:45:11,069
Što to znaci?
-Da previše igraš videoigrice.

391
00:45:11,230 --> 00:45:14,859
Prilican popis razlicitosti.

392
00:45:15,310 --> 00:45:18,108
Ti to meni hoceš
nešto reci...?

393
00:45:18,270 --> 00:45:21,387
Nemaš šanse, stari.
Ni u ludilu.

394
00:45:21,550 --> 00:45:24,587
Kužiš me? -Baš ti hvala.

395
00:45:24,750 --> 00:45:27,867
Uživaj u žalu
i okani se sranja.

396
00:45:28,190 --> 00:45:30,545
Hvala. -Nema na cemu.

397
00:45:36,430 --> 00:45:40,503
Pusti me na miru! -Mogu
ti pomoci. -Ne želim to!

398
00:45:40,670 --> 00:45:43,059
Brzo cu... -Ne!

399
00:45:43,350 --> 00:45:45,989
Moram na kopno!

400
00:45:48,310 --> 00:45:50,266
Boli me! Moram ici. Sal!

401
00:45:50,550 --> 00:45:54,463
Želiš na kopno? Da ti
zubar izvadi zub? -Da.

402
00:45:54,750 --> 00:45:56,468
Ne dolazi u obzir.

403
00:45:58,430 --> 00:46:00,944
Ja cu biti asistent.

404
00:46:04,510 --> 00:46:07,741
Kako ide, Richard? -Dobro.

405
00:46:08,510 --> 00:46:11,024
Shvacaš ovo? -Da.

406
00:46:11,710 --> 00:46:14,224
Tajna se mora cuvati, ne?

407
00:46:14,470 --> 00:46:17,428
Neki moraju pretrpjeti bol
da bi se tajna sacuvala.

408
00:46:18,630 --> 00:46:21,861
Sjajno. lzvrstan stav.

409
00:46:22,790 --> 00:46:24,667
Ma jasno.

410
00:46:27,070 --> 00:46:28,788
Sranje!

411
00:46:31,470 --> 00:46:33,461
Bravo.

412
00:46:34,510 --> 00:46:36,626
Daj mu za bol...

413
00:46:41,710 --> 00:46:44,099
Popij si malo.

414
00:46:45,910 --> 00:46:49,380
Bugs... Hvala ti.

415
00:46:56,270 --> 00:46:57,988
Richard?

416
00:46:59,990 --> 00:47:02,060
ldeš sa mnom na žal?

417
00:47:03,870 --> 00:47:06,623
Baci vec jednom!

418
00:47:08,430 --> 00:47:10,500
ldem.

419
00:47:20,430 --> 00:47:23,581
Jesi li sretan? -Sretan?

420
00:47:24,630 --> 00:47:27,428
Valjda.

421
00:47:27,670 --> 00:47:31,185
Fino mi je tu. Žal je super.

422
00:47:31,310 --> 00:47:33,426
Misliš li da te ignoriram?

423
00:47:36,030 --> 00:47:38,464
Ne. -Ali ignoriram te.

424
00:47:39,310 --> 00:47:43,428
S Etiennom sam; teško mi je
provoditi vrijeme s tobom.

425
00:47:51,350 --> 00:47:55,628
Nema ni razloga
zašto bi trebala.

426
00:47:57,230 --> 00:48:00,028
Provoditi vrijeme
sa mnom, mislim. -lma.

427
00:48:00,110 --> 00:48:02,465
Svidaš mi se. Jako.

428
00:48:03,470 --> 00:48:06,143
Rekla si to Etiennu?

429
00:48:06,390 --> 00:48:09,143
Ne. To je naša tajna.

430
00:48:12,390 --> 00:48:15,382
Gle! Plankton. Racici.

431
00:48:15,550 --> 00:48:18,462
Kada ih se uznemiri,
svijetle. Dodi.

432
00:49:25,390 --> 00:49:27,904
Te smo si noci obecali -

433
00:49:28,190 --> 00:49:31,739
i vjerovali u to -
da nitko nece saznati.

434
00:49:34,070 --> 00:49:36,220
Moramo razgovarati. -O cemu?

435
00:49:37,670 --> 00:49:42,186
O tebi i Francoise.
-Kako to misliš? Što o nama?

436
00:49:45,350 --> 00:49:47,227
Pa to, Richard,

437
00:49:48,390 --> 00:49:50,346
da želim da bude sretna.

438
00:49:50,590 --> 00:49:54,469
Jasno. Pa svi mi tu
to želimo, ne? -Šuti!

439
00:49:56,070 --> 00:49:57,981
Molim te, šuti.

440
00:50:03,070 --> 00:50:07,268
Ako je sretna s tobom,
necu joj smetati.

441
00:50:11,110 --> 00:50:17,140
Zbilja ne znam o cemu govoriš.
-Jebi se! Znam sve!

442
00:50:17,350 --> 00:50:20,467
Znam! l svi ostali znaju!

443
00:50:31,830 --> 00:50:34,503
Problem je vidjeti ribu.

444
00:50:35,630 --> 00:50:39,464
Uz jaku kišu i loše svjetlo
teško ih je uloviti.

445
00:50:40,790 --> 00:50:43,304
Kiša može padati danima.

446
00:50:43,470 --> 00:50:47,145
Katkad znamo biti
strašno gladni.

447
00:50:55,830 --> 00:50:57,388
Daj mi to.

448
00:50:59,310 --> 00:51:00,709
Richard!

449
00:51:30,510 --> 00:51:32,580
Ne cujem!

450
00:51:38,350 --> 00:51:40,386
Ni vi mene.

451
00:52:21,590 --> 00:52:26,380
Dobro! Mir.

452
00:52:27,990 --> 00:52:31,585
Prije nego pocnem,
upamtite neke stvari.

453
00:52:33,270 --> 00:52:36,740
Prvo, morate ostati
mirni. Kužite?

454
00:52:38,390 --> 00:52:42,941
Drugo, ne smijete
pokazati strah. -Pouci ih.

455
00:52:43,030 --> 00:52:46,784
Jer morski psi osjete strah

456
00:52:48,110 --> 00:52:50,749
kao što osjete i krv.

457
00:52:52,230 --> 00:52:56,064
Napao me,
što sam i ocekivao.

458
00:52:56,350 --> 00:53:00,662
Kako je priroda odredila.
Ralje razjapljene.

459
00:53:01,710 --> 00:53:05,749
Zubi oštri ko britve
blistaju pod vodom,

460
00:53:05,910 --> 00:53:08,185
poput dijamanata.

461
00:53:08,350 --> 00:53:12,423
A peraja ide naprijed-natrag
kako je jurio u napad.

462
00:53:13,550 --> 00:53:15,222
Kunem se Bogom,

463
00:53:15,470 --> 00:53:18,428
život mi je
bljesnuo pred ocima.

464
00:53:19,350 --> 00:53:22,740
Mogao sam se samo
voditi cistim refleksom.

465
00:53:23,710 --> 00:53:25,348
Cisti refleks.

466
00:53:25,510 --> 00:53:29,025
l urodeni instinkt
za preživljavanjem.

467
00:53:29,190 --> 00:53:32,899
l tako vikneš,
"Ne, danas necu umrijeti!"

468
00:53:37,470 --> 00:53:40,268
Bilo je: ili on ili ja.

469
00:53:40,710 --> 00:53:42,462
l on je to znao.

470
00:53:43,070 --> 00:53:44,822
l ja sam znao.

471
00:53:46,230 --> 00:53:50,826
Nema tu mržnje
ili necega takvog -

472
00:53:50,990 --> 00:53:53,458
u prirodi je to tako.

473
00:53:54,830 --> 00:53:57,264
Ali ako se dobro sjecam,

474
00:53:59,470 --> 00:54:02,906
kad mu se život gasio u ocima,

475
00:54:04,190 --> 00:54:07,262
u jednom sam
trenutku osjetio...

476
00:54:10,310 --> 00:54:12,619
da mi je rekao, Richard,

477
00:54:13,990 --> 00:54:16,265
uživaj u veceri.

478
00:54:28,510 --> 00:54:31,900
Cudno je iskustvo
ubiti morskog psa, ha?

479
00:54:34,590 --> 00:54:36,865
On je samo velika riba.

480
00:54:37,190 --> 00:54:40,102
Samo velika riba?! Možda.

481
00:54:40,270 --> 00:54:43,819
Možda kad je beba
i još ne zna ubijati.

482
00:54:43,990 --> 00:54:46,345
Tada možda jest
samo velika riba.

483
00:54:46,510 --> 00:54:50,469
Ali kad veliki bijeli,
nanjuši ljudsku krv...

484
00:54:50,630 --> 00:54:52,905
To je druga prica.

485
00:55:00,470 --> 00:55:02,665
O, Bože.

486
00:55:02,950 --> 00:55:07,387
Pa zar sam samo ja...
umoran od ove vrucine?

487
00:55:07,990 --> 00:55:10,424
lspricaj nam svoju drukciju,

488
00:55:10,510 --> 00:55:13,149
iako vrlo zanimljivu
pricu, drugi put.

489
00:55:17,510 --> 00:55:20,229
``Vrlo zanimljiva``. Keaty.

490
00:55:29,790 --> 00:55:32,862
laku noc, golupcici.
-Daj šuti.

491
00:55:33,190 --> 00:55:36,978
Neko smo vrijeme bili
nedodirljivi u svojoj sreci.

492
00:55:38,510 --> 00:55:41,229
Narode!

493
00:55:42,670 --> 00:55:44,467
Tiho!

494
00:55:44,710 --> 00:55:48,828
lmamo problem.
Nije katastrofa, ali...

495
00:55:49,110 --> 00:55:53,149
Nekoliko vreca riže
zaraženo je gljivicama.

496
00:55:57,590 --> 00:56:02,539
Netko ce morati otici
u Ko Pha Ngan po rižu.

497
00:56:06,190 --> 00:56:08,750
Nemojte tako revno...!

498
00:56:16,550 --> 00:56:18,620
Richard?

499
00:56:19,950 --> 00:56:24,068
Bi li išao sa mnom?
-Ne znam.

500
00:56:24,790 --> 00:56:28,465
ldem ja. -Ne, Bugs.
Richard ide, ne?

501
00:56:28,790 --> 00:56:31,702
Da? -Tko je za?

502
00:56:34,790 --> 00:56:37,588
Dobro. ldem u Ko Pha Ngan.

503
00:56:41,710 --> 00:56:45,988
Meni trebaju pasta
za zube i cetkica.

504
00:56:47,990 --> 00:56:50,345
Nove kupace gacice.
l novi šešir.

505
00:56:51,710 --> 00:56:53,302
Richard.

506
00:56:53,630 --> 00:56:57,942
Sto aspirina, sto paraceta-
mola, šest paketa tampona.

507
00:56:58,230 --> 00:57:01,267
Cetiri baterije AAA
i 20 kondoma.

508
00:57:01,390 --> 00:57:03,950
Ne, 40 kondoma. -l bocu votke.

509
00:57:04,190 --> 00:57:08,945
Šest cokolada.
l cetiri kutije tampona.

510
00:57:09,270 --> 00:57:10,703
Pomiriši.

511
00:57:10,830 --> 00:57:13,902
Još se osjeti riba.
Postajem riba!

512
00:57:14,070 --> 00:57:17,028
Obican sapun za obicne
ljude je niškoristi.

513
00:57:17,190 --> 00:57:20,660
Meni treba neki mnogo jaci.

514
00:57:21,190 --> 00:57:24,785
Konzervu govedine
s curryjem. -Mljac.

515
00:57:24,950 --> 00:57:28,067
Donesi baterija AAA
koliko nadeš.

516
00:57:28,230 --> 00:57:33,384
l novine. Daily Telegraph.
Radi kriketa.

517
00:57:35,990 --> 00:57:40,222
Mekog tariguza koliko
tu stane. -Tariguza?

518
00:57:40,390 --> 00:57:43,109
Caj od jasmina. Tigrovu
mast. Balzam za usne.

519
00:57:43,350 --> 00:57:45,864
Ulje cajevca. -lzbjeljivac.

520
00:57:46,030 --> 00:57:48,498
Regenerator za kosu.
Hidratantnu kremu.

521
00:57:48,670 --> 00:57:51,138
Nešto slatko. -12 Rizla.

522
00:57:51,270 --> 00:57:54,945
Kim. Šafran. Cimet.
-Dezic. Odstranjivac šminke.

523
00:58:02,230 --> 00:58:04,061
Što ti trebaš?

524
00:58:08,310 --> 00:58:11,108
U Ko Pha Nganu
drži ruke u džepovima,

525
00:58:11,270 --> 00:58:13,465
a pimpek u hlacama.

526
00:58:26,430 --> 00:58:30,582
Radovao sam se klima-
uredajima i hladnom pivu.

527
00:58:30,750 --> 00:58:32,661
Ali kad smo stigli...

528
00:58:33,550 --> 00:58:35,620
htio sam natrag.

529
00:58:35,990 --> 00:58:40,302
U trenu sam shvatio
zašto smo posebni,

530
00:58:40,790 --> 00:58:42,906
zašto cuvamo tajnu.

531
00:58:43,670 --> 00:58:46,423
lnace bi Otok,
prije ili poslije,

532
00:58:47,030 --> 00:58:48,861
postao ovakav!

533
00:58:55,590 --> 00:58:59,185
Rak. Paraziti.

534
00:59:03,950 --> 00:59:06,180
Proždiru cijeli svijet!

535
00:59:16,030 --> 00:59:19,102
Par mjeseci.
Možda godinu dana.

536
00:59:20,230 --> 00:59:22,221
Da, zbilja.

537
00:59:22,950 --> 00:59:27,102
Ne, super je tu. Drukcije.

538
00:59:28,470 --> 00:59:30,620
Drukcije, velim.

539
00:59:32,590 --> 00:59:35,662
Ne, nazvat cu
ja tebe. Obecavam.

540
00:59:37,750 --> 00:59:40,628
l ti meni fališ. Može.

541
00:59:41,070 --> 00:59:43,538
Dobro. Bog.

542
00:59:51,350 --> 00:59:52,988
Zbogom.

543
00:59:53,630 --> 00:59:56,144
Kakva ti se cini stvarnost?

544
00:59:56,310 --> 00:59:59,780
Nije kakvu je pamtim...
-Svaki je put sve gore.

545
01:00:02,150 --> 01:00:06,826
lpak jest Richard!
Kako si, stari?

546
01:00:08,230 --> 01:00:12,018
Sammy, dodi! -Što ima, stari?

547
01:00:12,190 --> 01:00:14,340
Sada cete ga upoznati.

548
01:00:14,550 --> 01:00:17,144
Hilda. Eva. Richard.

549
01:00:17,310 --> 01:00:19,380
Tip s kartom.

550
01:00:20,590 --> 01:00:23,309
l one idu s nama.

551
01:00:24,350 --> 01:00:27,422
Malo se odužilo;
uživali smo...

552
01:00:27,590 --> 01:00:31,902
Decki... zeznuo sam se.
-Kako to misliš?

553
01:00:32,070 --> 01:00:34,538
Onaj Žal ne postoji.

554
01:00:34,710 --> 01:00:37,270
lpak smo te našli.
-Nema žala?

555
01:00:37,430 --> 01:00:42,629
Ne. Karta je lažnjak.
Bio si u pravu: tek legenda.

556
01:00:42,790 --> 01:00:46,260
Mit. Ozbiljno. Ne postoji.

557
01:00:46,430 --> 01:00:50,981
Karta je lažnjak. Kužite.
-Muljaš nam, ne?

558
01:00:51,150 --> 01:00:54,984
Tamo je sigurno raj!
-Ne postoji.

559
01:00:55,150 --> 01:01:00,986
Što? Mislim da nas zajebava.
-Velim, zaboravi, šupcino!

560
01:01:03,830 --> 01:01:06,947
Nikad ti više
necu platiti pivo.

561
01:01:09,750 --> 01:01:11,945
Rekao si im kamo ideš?

562
01:01:14,990 --> 01:01:16,901
Vidjeli su kartu?

563
01:01:21,070 --> 01:01:23,379
lmaju kopiju? -Ne.

564
01:01:33,230 --> 01:01:36,984
Dobro. Malo cemo se odmoriti.

565
01:01:39,190 --> 01:01:42,068
Sumnjam da bi
uspjeli doci na Otok.

566
01:01:42,670 --> 01:01:45,309
Ali necemo nikome
ništa reci.

567
01:01:46,790 --> 01:01:50,305
Neka to ostane
medu nama. -Hvala.

568
01:01:52,350 --> 01:01:54,420
Ništa.

569
01:02:00,390 --> 01:02:04,303
Ja cu malo igrati
bilijar sa Sumet.

570
01:02:07,830 --> 01:02:10,902
Ti idi ugrijati krevet.

571
01:02:52,110 --> 01:02:53,782
Sal?

572
01:02:56,390 --> 01:02:58,187
Sal?

573
01:03:01,470 --> 01:03:03,745
Može pitanje?

574
01:03:04,670 --> 01:03:06,820
Bilo je super.

575
01:03:07,950 --> 01:03:10,100
Nisam to mislio.

576
01:03:11,150 --> 01:03:13,106
O Bugsu.

577
01:03:17,910 --> 01:03:19,502
Dobro.

578
01:03:20,230 --> 01:03:22,300
Ovako stvari stoje:

579
01:03:22,470 --> 01:03:24,825
Bugs je moj decko.

580
01:03:25,750 --> 01:03:27,820
Moj partner.

581
01:03:28,190 --> 01:03:31,865
A s tobom sam se
samo poševila.

582
01:03:33,230 --> 01:03:36,461
U redu? -U redu.

583
01:03:37,110 --> 01:03:39,863
Skroz u redu. -Fino.

584
01:03:40,110 --> 01:03:43,625
Spavaj. Možda se opet
narajcam prije dorucka.

585
01:04:07,230 --> 01:04:08,982
Dogovorili smo se -

586
01:04:09,430 --> 01:04:12,467
nece nikome reci za kartu,

587
01:04:12,550 --> 01:04:14,666
a ja sam platio
njezinu šutnju

588
01:04:14,750 --> 01:04:16,627
i mogucnost povratka.

589
01:04:16,910 --> 01:04:19,708
Nisam htio ni misliti
na pravu cijenu...

590
01:04:39,750 --> 01:04:42,708
Držiš? -Držim!

591
01:04:58,910 --> 01:05:04,064
lmaš izbjeljivac?
-l odstranjivac šminke.

592
01:05:07,030 --> 01:05:10,181
Obožavam te!

593
01:05:12,790 --> 01:05:15,224
Sjajno! Super.

594
01:05:15,510 --> 01:05:17,341
Kupio si baterije? -Tu su.

595
01:05:19,470 --> 01:05:22,985
Sten, za tebe.
Christo, za tebe.

596
01:05:23,070 --> 01:05:25,584
Hej, Ricardo! Hvala.

597
01:05:25,790 --> 01:05:27,587
Govedina s curryjem.

598
01:05:38,110 --> 01:05:41,022
Kartonski fotic
za jednokratnu uporabu.

599
01:05:41,990 --> 01:05:46,108
Nije kao onaj tvoj... l morat
ceš cekati na razvijanje.

600
01:05:46,270 --> 01:05:49,546
Nema veze. Super je.

601
01:05:51,590 --> 01:05:56,948
Što je? -Kako je bilo?
-Dobro. Bez problema.

602
01:05:57,950 --> 01:06:03,343
Mislila sam, sa Sal. -Dobro.
Dobro se slažemo.

603
01:06:06,510 --> 01:06:09,422
Prica se da joj se svidaš.

604
01:06:09,870 --> 01:06:12,828
Sranje. Nisam primijetio.

605
01:06:14,110 --> 01:06:16,624
Ništa nije bilo?
-Jasno da nije.

606
01:06:18,070 --> 01:06:20,026
Casna rijec?

607
01:06:20,550 --> 01:06:22,939
Bio sam tako sretan
što sam se vratio

608
01:06:23,070 --> 01:06:25,584
da nisam htio
uništiti trenutak.

609
01:06:25,790 --> 01:06:28,668
Da. Casna rijec.

610
01:06:44,310 --> 01:06:46,187
Falila si mi.

611
01:06:47,630 --> 01:06:50,940
Narode, ovamo! Molim vas!

612
01:06:54,310 --> 01:06:57,507
Bliže malo. Molim vas.

613
01:07:00,310 --> 01:07:03,461
Približite se. Pogledajte me.

614
01:07:06,110 --> 01:07:09,068
1 ... 2... 3.

615
01:07:11,710 --> 01:07:14,588
Nastavili smo
gdje smo stali.

616
01:07:14,910 --> 01:07:17,743
Kao da nikamo
nisam ni išao.

617
01:07:18,790 --> 01:07:20,382
Recimo.

618
01:07:47,870 --> 01:07:50,100
Morski pas!

619
01:08:18,510 --> 01:08:20,740
Ne urlaj!

620
01:08:51,910 --> 01:08:54,708
Moja... noga.

621
01:09:07,670 --> 01:09:11,299
Pomozi mi. -Odvest cemo te
u bolnicu. To može.

622
01:09:11,470 --> 01:09:15,179
Ali nemoj nikome
reci gdje te napao.

623
01:09:15,350 --> 01:09:17,705
Moramo sacuvati tajnu.

624
01:09:18,750 --> 01:09:20,627
Što govori?

625
01:09:20,750 --> 01:09:23,947
Da dovedemo lijecnika ovamo.

626
01:09:24,150 --> 01:09:29,702
Boji se vode. -Znam. Ali ne
možemo nikoga dovesti ovamo.

627
01:09:29,910 --> 01:09:32,788
Moraš dovesti pomoc!
-Ne možemo!

628
01:09:32,990 --> 01:09:36,221
Moraš ici. lli ostati,
pa što bude.

629
01:09:39,150 --> 01:09:41,664
Tko je protiv?

630
01:09:43,190 --> 01:09:45,181
Što kaže?

631
01:09:46,470 --> 01:09:49,143
Pita što mu je s prijateljem.

632
01:09:54,310 --> 01:09:58,588
Danas odajemo posljednju
pocast našem Stenu.

633
01:10:00,310 --> 01:10:02,221
Neka Bog uzme tvoju dušu,

634
01:10:02,670 --> 01:10:05,104
pocivaj u vjecnome miru.

635
01:10:09,910 --> 01:10:11,502
Falit ceš nam.

636
01:10:14,470 --> 01:10:16,984
Od Christa i mene.

637
01:10:20,390 --> 01:10:22,142
(Pocivaj u miru.)

638
01:10:41,550 --> 01:10:45,304
STARl ME GUSARl UKRALl

639
01:10:46,470 --> 01:10:49,064
l PRODALl TRGOVACKOM BRODU

640
01:10:50,590 --> 01:10:53,229
ClM SU ME UZELl

641
01:10:54,390 --> 01:10:56,984
lZ JAZBlNE BEZ DNA

642
01:10:57,310 --> 01:11:01,019
MOJA JE RUKA POSTALA JACA

643
01:11:01,190 --> 01:11:04,705
POMOCU BOŽJE RUKE

644
01:11:05,270 --> 01:11:08,945
Ml lDEMO NAPRlJED
U OVOJ GENERAClJl

645
01:11:09,790 --> 01:11:12,668
POBJEDONOSNO

646
01:11:13,790 --> 01:11:16,509
ZAPJEVAJTE SA MNOM

647
01:11:18,390 --> 01:11:21,063
OVE PJESME SLOBODE

648
01:11:21,510 --> 01:11:26,265
JER SVE ŠTO CU
lKAD lMATl SU

649
01:11:26,470 --> 01:11:29,542
PJESME OTKUPLJENJA...

650
01:11:46,950 --> 01:11:50,625
Poslije ukopa, pokušavali
smo živjeti kao prije,

651
01:11:51,630 --> 01:11:53,746
ali nije išlo...

652
01:11:54,830 --> 01:11:57,981
skoro je postalo jasno
da je problem Christo.

653
01:11:58,910 --> 01:12:01,424
Ne opet. -Šuti!

654
01:12:02,110 --> 01:12:04,180
Kod napada morskoga psa,

655
01:12:04,350 --> 01:12:06,386
ili bilo koje
vece tragedije,

656
01:12:06,590 --> 01:12:09,627
važno je biti
pojeden i umrijeti -

657
01:12:09,990 --> 01:12:14,905
onda te pokopaju i svi
kažu da si bio super.

658
01:12:16,230 --> 01:12:20,109
lli... oporaviš se,
i svi to zaborave.

659
01:12:20,350 --> 01:12:23,342
Ne mogu to podnijeti.
-Christo, molim te...

660
01:12:31,390 --> 01:12:33,824
Oporaviti se ili umrijeti.

661
01:12:34,270 --> 01:12:38,229
Kada si negdje izmedu,
to ljude ljuti.

662
01:12:39,630 --> 01:12:43,179
Ne možete ga ostaviti!
To je odvratno!

663
01:12:43,750 --> 01:12:46,548
Odnesite ga natrag. -Tu smo...

664
01:12:46,990 --> 01:12:49,106
Životinje!

665
01:12:50,550 --> 01:12:52,666
Zašto to radite?

666
01:12:53,310 --> 01:12:54,982
Recite mi!

667
01:12:56,110 --> 01:12:58,180
Kako možete?!

668
01:13:02,310 --> 01:13:03,982
Richard...

669
01:13:06,430 --> 01:13:08,500
Gadovi jebeni!

670
01:13:10,430 --> 01:13:12,341
Gadovi!

671
01:13:12,510 --> 01:13:15,468
Bilo bi lakše osuditi
naše ponašanje

672
01:13:15,630 --> 01:13:19,100
da nije tako ucinkovito.
No, Daleko od oka -

673
01:13:19,430 --> 01:13:21,739
daleko od srca...

674
01:13:21,950 --> 01:13:25,465
Kada ga više nije bilo,
bilo nam je lakše.

675
01:13:26,910 --> 01:13:30,266
Na Žalu je lako
okrenuti leda,

676
01:13:30,710 --> 01:13:33,144
ali nije uvijek
lako zaboraviti...

677
01:14:12,070 --> 01:14:16,188
Damo im dolare! Jebemo im
kceri! l sjebemo im zemlju!

678
01:14:18,910 --> 01:14:21,424
Richard... Podi sa mnom.

679
01:14:32,910 --> 01:14:35,378
Je li to ili nije

680
01:14:35,990 --> 01:14:39,460
karta u njezinim rukama?

681
01:14:40,550 --> 01:14:43,462
Jesi li ili nisi

682
01:14:44,910 --> 01:14:46,662
napravio kopiju?

683
01:14:48,190 --> 01:14:50,658
Ne muci me laž.

684
01:14:51,750 --> 01:14:55,060
Ali ta karta znaci nevolju!

685
01:14:55,230 --> 01:14:58,427
Sjecaš se onih
farmera s puškama?

686
01:14:58,670 --> 01:15:03,027
Rekli su nam da nitko
više ne smije doci.

687
01:15:03,510 --> 01:15:07,185
A ispada da dijelimo
turisticke vodice!

688
01:15:08,830 --> 01:15:10,821
Sal...

689
01:15:11,390 --> 01:15:14,939
Objasnit cemo im. Reci
da im je Daffy dao kartu.

690
01:15:15,670 --> 01:15:17,945
``Objasniti``?!

691
01:15:21,910 --> 01:15:25,425
Sjedi tu i cuvaj
stražu dok ne dodu.

692
01:15:25,590 --> 01:15:29,503
Tu?! -Da, tu.
l onda im uzmi kartu.

693
01:15:29,950 --> 01:15:33,784
Kako znaš i umiješ!
-Sal, cekaj!

694
01:15:33,990 --> 01:15:37,585
Mogu tjednima biti
ondje! -Da. Cekaj ih.

695
01:15:37,750 --> 01:15:42,062
l što da radim kada
dodu? -Uzmi im kartu!

696
01:15:42,310 --> 01:15:46,940
Ti si im je dao!
Sad je uzmi i uvjeri da odu!

697
01:15:53,990 --> 01:15:56,788
Svima ceš reci...?

698
01:16:03,990 --> 01:16:06,584
E ovo je stvarno
bilo sranje.

699
01:16:06,830 --> 01:16:10,459
Ni ja, kao ni Sal,
nisam htio da dodu.

700
01:16:10,710 --> 01:16:13,144
Što je htjela od mene?

701
01:16:13,270 --> 01:16:17,058
Da ih otjeram? Da im
prijetim? Cime i kako?!

702
01:16:17,230 --> 01:16:20,461
Do kada dodu, mogao
sam umrijeti od gladi.

703
01:16:22,070 --> 01:16:24,982
Sal? Makni svjetlo...

704
01:16:25,190 --> 01:16:26,828
Svinjo!

705
01:16:27,150 --> 01:16:30,028
Nisam ništa mogao!

706
01:16:30,190 --> 01:16:33,307
Moram tu biti!
-Ne radi se o tome!

707
01:16:33,470 --> 01:16:36,667
Nego? -O Sal i tebi
u Ko Pha Ngan.

708
01:16:39,070 --> 01:16:41,379
Ah, to. -Da, to!

709
01:16:41,550 --> 01:16:45,065
Svima je rekla.
A ja posljednja saznam!?

710
01:16:45,230 --> 01:16:47,869
Ona je bar
iskrena. Ne kao ti.

711
01:16:51,190 --> 01:16:54,739
Francoise, ja...
Sto da ti kažem...

712
01:16:56,150 --> 01:16:58,789
Nema se tu što reci.

713
01:17:04,030 --> 01:17:08,262
Hvala ti... Hvala što si mi
život ucinila savršenim!

714
01:17:10,350 --> 01:17:12,022
Super!

715
01:17:12,270 --> 01:17:15,103
K vragu!

716
01:17:16,870 --> 01:17:18,747
Jebemu!

717
01:17:20,190 --> 01:17:21,669
Koji sam ja idiot!

718
01:17:25,830 --> 01:17:29,743
Znao sam da ce
kad-tad saznati.

719
01:17:30,070 --> 01:17:32,425
l valjda sam to zavrijedio.

720
01:17:32,630 --> 01:17:35,827
Mogao sam joj dati sve
isprike koje je željela,

721
01:17:36,030 --> 01:17:40,820
ali što bih imao
od toga... No super!

722
01:17:42,950 --> 01:17:46,022
lsprva sam mislio
da cu tu umrijeti.

723
01:17:46,270 --> 01:17:48,989
Da ce mi se
svijet raspasti.

724
01:17:53,630 --> 01:17:55,507
Ali nije.

725
01:18:05,710 --> 01:18:08,099
Zapravo, uskoro sam

726
01:18:08,230 --> 01:18:11,267
našao mnogo toga
što me zainteresiralo.

727
01:18:11,870 --> 01:18:16,705
l ubrzo sam shvatio
da ljubav, poput tuge,

728
01:18:17,150 --> 01:18:21,780
izblijedi, a zamijeni je
nešto uzbudljivije.

729
01:18:27,310 --> 01:18:30,700
Život na brdu postao
je veliko poboljšanje.

730
01:18:30,870 --> 01:18:36,149
Radio sam što sam htio.
Bez ikakvih obveza.

731
01:18:36,310 --> 01:18:39,302
Nije me gnjavio ni Bugs,
ni Etienne ni Francoise.

732
01:18:39,430 --> 01:18:41,785
Sad sam ja bio glavna faca.

733
01:18:41,950 --> 01:18:44,384
Nisam se imao zašto vracati.

734
01:19:13,190 --> 01:19:16,262
lGRA ZAVRŠENA
POKUŠAJ PONOVNO

735
01:19:29,590 --> 01:19:32,229
Samo sam se zafrkavao.

736
01:19:34,750 --> 01:19:37,822
No što sam duže
bio daleko od njih,

737
01:19:38,030 --> 01:19:40,225
manje su mi falili.

738
01:19:50,110 --> 01:19:52,704
A našao sam i nove igrace

739
01:19:53,310 --> 01:19:56,063
iako to oni još nisu znali.

740
01:20:45,710 --> 01:20:48,622
Ova je šuma moj teritorij.

741
01:20:51,950 --> 01:20:55,101
Zadatak mi je bio
dokopati se karte.

742
01:20:58,430 --> 01:21:01,502
A ovo su bili...
moji branitelji.

743
01:21:05,150 --> 01:21:07,664
Jedino sam ja vidio

744
01:21:08,670 --> 01:21:11,025
kako se sve uklapa.

745
01:21:13,830 --> 01:21:15,582
Otok.

746
01:21:17,830 --> 01:21:19,468
Ja.

747
01:21:21,190 --> 01:21:22,782
Oni.

748
01:21:24,910 --> 01:21:27,105
Uljezi.

749
01:21:33,150 --> 01:21:35,220
Sve spojeno.

750
01:21:36,630 --> 01:21:38,985
Svi igramo istu igru.

751
01:21:42,670 --> 01:21:46,379
A u središtu svega
jedan covjek -

752
01:21:50,910 --> 01:21:52,866
Daffy.

753
01:22:10,510 --> 01:22:12,307
Upadaj!

754
01:22:15,950 --> 01:22:18,100
Pogledaj, Richard!

755
01:22:18,710 --> 01:22:21,668
Virusi, Richard! Rak!

756
01:22:22,110 --> 01:22:26,342
Debele svinje proždiru
svijet! Baš tu!

757
01:22:27,150 --> 01:22:29,823
Na Žalu! Na ulicama.

758
01:22:30,070 --> 01:22:33,301
Damo im dolare
i jebemo im kceri!

759
01:22:34,830 --> 01:22:37,981
Pocinje s cetvero.
Ali razmnože se!

760
01:22:38,150 --> 01:22:40,380
Moramo ih zaustaviti!

761
01:22:43,910 --> 01:22:46,708
Sve uništiti!

762
01:22:47,110 --> 01:22:49,021
Sve...?!

763
01:22:49,790 --> 01:22:53,988
Jesi li za ili protiv
mene? -Za tebe, Daffy!

764
01:23:15,750 --> 01:23:17,502
Richard?!

765
01:23:18,470 --> 01:23:20,301
Gdje si bio?

766
01:23:22,070 --> 01:23:24,061
Zašto sjediš u mraku?

767
01:23:25,270 --> 01:23:28,546
Vježbam vid nocu. -Zašto?

768
01:23:30,750 --> 01:23:32,627
Znaš o cemu cesto mislim?

769
01:23:34,510 --> 01:23:36,341
Nemam pojma.

770
01:23:40,270 --> 01:23:43,148
O Daffyju. -Daffyju?

771
01:23:49,990 --> 01:23:51,901
Divim mu se.

772
01:23:52,790 --> 01:23:56,829
Jedva si ga poznavao. -Tocno.

773
01:23:59,750 --> 01:24:01,980
Ali imao je stila.

774
01:24:06,790 --> 01:24:08,508
Dodi.

775
01:24:08,750 --> 01:24:11,059
Dodi ovamo!

776
01:24:13,390 --> 01:24:15,506
Razgovaraju o tebi.

777
01:24:21,190 --> 01:24:25,741
Kakav savjet hoceš?
Ocito je samo usamljen.

778
01:24:25,910 --> 01:24:28,299
Zanima me što ga muci.
-Misliš da je meni drag?

779
01:24:28,470 --> 01:24:31,109
Što radi cijeli dan?
-Ne peca. -Ne radi u vrtu.

780
01:24:31,270 --> 01:24:33,545
Ali krade nam
hranu. Sigurno.

781
01:24:33,750 --> 01:24:39,222
Cuješ? -Besposlen. Parazit.
Beskoristan kreten.

782
01:24:39,630 --> 01:24:41,985
Sredi se.

783
01:24:42,150 --> 01:24:45,108
Ne možeš samo švrljati
i ni sa kim razgovarati.

784
01:24:45,310 --> 01:24:48,620
Što izigravaš?
Sto ti se dogodilo?

785
01:24:48,790 --> 01:24:51,145
Nedavno si još bio u redu.

786
01:24:51,350 --> 01:24:54,899
Koji ti je kurac?!
Pogledaj se!

787
01:24:55,390 --> 01:24:58,780
Sada pricaš o Daffyju?
Bio je ludak!

788
01:24:58,950 --> 01:25:02,465
Puk`o covjek. Ubio se.
Richard...

789
01:25:03,910 --> 01:25:07,539
Richard! Cuješ li ti mene?

790
01:25:09,030 --> 01:25:13,421
Nemoj završiti kao on.
Ne možeš se tako ponašati!

791
01:25:13,510 --> 01:25:15,785
Ostani s nama.

792
01:25:15,950 --> 01:25:21,308
Dobri su. Pricaju o tebi
jer si sjeban. Sredi se.

793
01:26:05,630 --> 01:26:07,746
Gljivu, Richard?

794
01:26:09,750 --> 01:26:11,866
Ne, hvala, Daffy.

795
01:26:12,670 --> 01:26:15,468
l bez toga vidim
kako stvari stoje.

796
01:26:15,710 --> 01:26:19,259
Drago mi je cuti.
-Glava mi mora biti bistra.

797
01:26:19,430 --> 01:26:23,139
Sukob se približava.
-Uništenje? -Bravo, mali.

798
01:26:24,670 --> 01:26:26,661
Znaš što?

799
01:26:27,190 --> 01:26:29,306
Ti si mi pokazao put.

800
01:26:30,190 --> 01:26:31,987
Pokazao mi istinu.

801
01:26:35,430 --> 01:26:37,864
Više nije važno
što ja mislim.

802
01:26:38,070 --> 01:26:41,619
Sada ovisi o tebi.
-Necu te razocarati.

803
01:26:42,390 --> 01:26:45,143
Richard... Bez uvrede, ali...

804
01:26:46,310 --> 01:26:48,699
Malo si sjeban u glavu, ne?

805
01:26:55,590 --> 01:26:58,263
Drago mi je što
sam te upoznao.

806
01:29:52,390 --> 01:29:54,426
Gle ovo! ldemo!

807
01:30:15,350 --> 01:30:18,467
Ovo mora biti
narkomanski raj!

808
01:30:22,630 --> 01:30:25,383
PUŠlM DVA JOlNTA
SVAKOG JUTRA

809
01:30:25,550 --> 01:30:29,668
DVA NOCU, DVA POSllJE-
POPODNE; l BAS JE SUPER

810
01:30:30,390 --> 01:30:34,065
DVA U DOBA MlRA
l DVA KADA JE RAT

811
01:30:34,310 --> 01:30:38,622
DVA PRlJE DRUGA DVA
l ONDA JOŠ KOJl!

812
01:30:51,750 --> 01:30:53,741
Bog. -Sranje.

813
01:30:55,750 --> 01:30:57,661
Amerikanci smo.

814
01:30:58,470 --> 01:31:01,030
Turisti. -Amerikanci.

815
01:31:01,550 --> 01:31:05,384
lmali smo kartu...
l došli ovamo...

816
01:31:05,750 --> 01:31:09,140
Ali pogriješili
smo. Žao nam je.

817
01:31:09,550 --> 01:31:11,347
Odlazimo.

818
01:31:17,070 --> 01:31:20,187
Dobro? Odlazimo.

819
01:31:26,350 --> 01:31:29,945
Samo želimo otici.
-Daj im nešto love.

820
01:31:31,030 --> 01:31:35,262
lmam americke dolare!
Hocete americki novac?

821
01:31:36,350 --> 01:31:37,829
Evo.

822
01:31:39,390 --> 01:31:41,142
Uzmite.

823
01:31:43,550 --> 01:31:46,826
lmam i sat. Svira.

824
01:34:18,510 --> 01:34:20,978
Ovo nam je šesta godina!

825
01:34:26,030 --> 01:34:28,260
Želim gledati unaprijed

826
01:34:29,390 --> 01:34:33,986
jer vidim da iza
problema koje smo imali...

827
01:34:35,790 --> 01:34:38,258
lza problema koje smo imali

828
01:34:40,230 --> 01:34:44,428
tu imamo mnogo toga
što nas nadahnjuje.

829
01:34:45,150 --> 01:34:47,823
Ne govorim samo o Otoku.

830
01:34:49,630 --> 01:34:51,382
Nego o vama.

831
01:34:52,870 --> 01:34:55,782
Vi ste razlog
uspjeha naše zajednice.

832
01:34:57,510 --> 01:34:59,501
A uspješna je.

833
01:35:01,830 --> 01:35:04,947
Htio sam se sjetiti
kakav sam bio prije.

834
01:35:05,910 --> 01:35:08,470
Ali nisam uspio.
-Za Otok!

835
01:35:09,910 --> 01:35:12,708
Za vas!
-Dok sam ovdje...

836
01:35:13,030 --> 01:35:17,387
Za buducnost!
-Ne mogu biti kao nekada.

837
01:35:34,950 --> 01:35:39,785
Moramo razgovarati. Slušaj!
Moramo razgovarati! Stani!

838
01:35:40,350 --> 01:35:42,910
Slušaj! Moramo razgovarati!

839
01:35:43,230 --> 01:35:45,949
Slušaj me! Moramo razgovarati!

840
01:35:46,310 --> 01:35:51,065
Prestani, k vragu! Prestani!

841
01:35:51,550 --> 01:35:54,018
Necu ti ništa!

842
01:35:54,510 --> 01:35:58,503
Ja sam. Richard. Sjecaš me se?

843
01:35:59,950 --> 01:36:03,989
Onaj koji ne zna igrati
nogomet. Onaj bez cure.

844
01:36:06,430 --> 01:36:08,307
Sjecam se.

845
01:36:09,230 --> 01:36:12,745
Neko vrijeme nisam
bio tu. To je sve.

846
01:36:13,910 --> 01:36:15,707
To je sve.

847
01:36:25,390 --> 01:36:27,858
Slušajte! Sve se sjebalo!

848
01:36:28,030 --> 01:36:30,544
Ubili su cetvero ljudi.
Tko zna što još kane!

849
01:36:30,670 --> 01:36:33,980
Moramo smjesta otici!
Samo nas troje.

850
01:36:34,190 --> 01:36:36,181
Kao prije.

851
01:36:38,830 --> 01:36:40,866
Ne mogu ga ostaviti.

852
01:36:41,550 --> 01:36:45,828
Povest cemo i njega.
-Ali, pogledaj ga.

853
01:36:46,790 --> 01:36:51,341
Ne možemo ga micati.
Gangrena. Siri se.

854
01:36:52,310 --> 01:36:54,346
Umrijet ce.

855
01:37:04,390 --> 01:37:06,620
Cekajte me u camcu.

856
01:37:49,750 --> 01:37:53,663
Christo je morao patiti
da bi drugi uživali.

857
01:37:56,470 --> 01:37:58,700
Na savršenom Žalu

858
01:37:58,910 --> 01:38:01,868
ništa ne smije prekinuti
potragu za užitkom.

859
01:38:03,110 --> 01:38:04,941
Cak ni umiranje.

860
01:39:15,230 --> 01:39:17,903
Mislite da vas
želim ozlijediti?

861
01:39:18,350 --> 01:39:21,023
Ja sam samo farmer.

862
01:39:21,430 --> 01:39:23,227
Razumijete?

863
01:39:23,990 --> 01:39:25,548
Radim.

864
01:39:26,870 --> 01:39:29,338
Šaljem novac obitelji.

865
01:39:31,670 --> 01:39:34,980
Kada bi previše ljudi
došlo na Otok,

866
01:39:35,390 --> 01:39:37,665
to bi za mene bila nevolja.

867
01:39:38,510 --> 01:39:40,262
Ako ne mogu raditi,

868
01:39:41,350 --> 01:39:45,104
ne mogu slati novac
obitelji. Gladovali bi.

869
01:39:47,510 --> 01:39:49,740
Rekao sam, nitko više.

870
01:39:51,350 --> 01:39:53,261
Ali novi su došli.

871
01:39:55,750 --> 01:39:57,183
A ti...

872
01:39:58,590 --> 01:40:01,058
Ti si im dala kartu!

873
01:40:05,630 --> 01:40:08,667
Sada... Svi idite doma.

874
01:40:09,270 --> 01:40:12,865
Zaboravite ovaj otok.
Zaboravite Tajland.

875
01:40:13,390 --> 01:40:15,301
Razumijete?

876
01:40:16,230 --> 01:40:19,108
Razumijete? -Ne.

877
01:40:20,470 --> 01:40:23,143
Što? -Ne.

878
01:40:25,510 --> 01:40:27,341
Ne idemo.

879
01:40:28,110 --> 01:40:30,305
Ovo je i naš dom!

880
01:40:30,670 --> 01:40:34,424
Naša kuca. Sami
smo je sagradili!

881
01:40:34,630 --> 01:40:36,825
Nikamo ne odlazimo!

882
01:40:37,310 --> 01:40:39,460
Daj, Sal...

883
01:40:39,910 --> 01:40:44,188
Mislim da griješiš. Zbilja...

884
01:40:45,750 --> 01:40:49,186
Ako kaže da moramo
ici... -Šuti, Richard!

885
01:40:51,510 --> 01:40:53,785
lonako si ti za sve kriv.

886
01:40:55,470 --> 01:40:57,904
Tko je kopirao kartu?!

887
01:41:10,510 --> 01:41:12,819
Ti si mudar momak.

888
01:41:13,910 --> 01:41:17,186
Šuljaš se okolo. -Pusti ga!

889
01:41:17,990 --> 01:41:22,586
Kradeš nam. lgraš se
našim oružjem.

890
01:41:46,870 --> 01:41:49,942
Ako želiš ostati...

891
01:41:54,590 --> 01:41:57,024
Ako želiš ostati!

892
01:42:18,590 --> 01:42:23,505
Nemoj, Sal! Slušaj...
Ne budi luda!

893
01:42:24,230 --> 01:42:29,429
Spusti pištolj.
-Ti si nam donio nevolje.

894
01:42:30,870 --> 01:42:34,545
Ne možeš, Sal! -Zaustavite je!

895
01:42:36,990 --> 01:42:39,902
Keaty! Pomozi!

896
01:42:44,550 --> 01:42:47,428
Jebite se, gadovi prokleti!

897
01:42:49,150 --> 01:42:54,622
Daj, Sal! Hajde! Pucaj!

898
01:42:54,790 --> 01:42:59,466
Ne možeš, Sal! -Zacepi!
-Ako povuceš obarac, Sal,

899
01:42:59,790 --> 01:43:04,910
sve je gotovo!
-Daj. -Jer ovaj put

900
01:43:05,470 --> 01:43:09,509
nije kao s Christom, koji
trune gdje ga ne vidimo.

901
01:43:09,750 --> 01:43:12,662
Nije kao s cetvero
koji su danas ubijeni.

902
01:43:13,350 --> 01:43:17,389
Ovaj put svi moraju gledati

903
01:43:18,190 --> 01:43:23,583
što se sve radi da naš
mali raj ostane tajnom.

904
01:43:23,790 --> 01:43:27,669
Gledajte! -Šuti!
-Gledajte kako me ubija!

905
01:43:27,830 --> 01:43:32,540
Hajde, Sal! Neka vide krv!

906
01:43:33,590 --> 01:43:36,741
Da vidimo mogu li
podnijeti. -Nemoj!

907
01:43:40,990 --> 01:43:43,140
Oni mogu podnijeti.

908
01:44:14,950 --> 01:44:19,546
Ne! Ne!

909
01:44:41,750 --> 01:44:46,301
lgra je gotova.
Ali ona nije htjela otici.

910
01:44:47,670 --> 01:44:51,299
Odvec je vjerovala
da bi se promijenila.

911
01:44:51,790 --> 01:44:54,258
Tako smo je
tocno tu ostavili.

912
01:45:23,430 --> 01:45:27,503
A mi ostali
nosili smo svoje grijehe

913
01:45:27,670 --> 01:45:31,106
i vratili se onome
što smo zvali domom

914
01:45:31,270 --> 01:45:34,307
da nastavimo tamo
gdje smo stali...

915
01:45:42,870 --> 01:45:46,067
Nikad ne zaboravimo
što smo ucinili.

916
01:45:46,270 --> 01:45:48,261
Ali prilagodimo se.

917
01:45:48,630 --> 01:45:50,507
Živimo dalje.

918
01:46:24,550 --> 01:46:28,179
lME ClANA:
lOZlNKA:

919
01:46:29,510 --> 01:46:32,183
Želite nešto? -Ne, hvala.

920
01:46:32,350 --> 01:46:36,423
Aja? PROVJERA POŠTE
Još vjerujem u raj.

921
01:46:37,470 --> 01:46:40,667
Ali sada znam da ga
se ne može tražiti.

922
01:46:40,830 --> 01:46:44,823
ŠAlJU: MAMA l TATA
Ne radi se kamo ideš.

923
01:46:45,110 --> 01:46:48,944
Nego kako se osjecaš
kad si dio necega.

924
01:46:49,190 --> 01:46:51,704
ŽlVOT NA ŽAlU

